				</p>

					<br>
				</article>
				<img src="./gandivacar.jpg" alt="team aurora" class="w-1/2 transition duration-300 ease-in-out hover:scale-110 duration-700 delay-150 relative transform transition-all opacity-0 translate-y-12 ease-out" data-replace='{ "translate-y-12": "translate-y-0", "opacity-0": "opacity-100" }'>
